Madam Julianah Ibimawu Lawrence is dead. She died on Monday at 86, according to a statement by one of her children, Mr Eniola Bello, Managing Director/Editor-in-Chief of ThisDay. Born in Odolu Kabba, Kogi State on August 18, 1933, the deceased touched many lives in the community with her life of generosity, kindness and self-sacrifice. She is survived by five children – Mrs Victoria Bosede Ogunbiyi, Commodore Ayo Bello-Odofin (rtd), Mr. Eniola Bello, Mrs Olabisi SamVictor, and Mr. Olaofe Odofin – many grandchildren and great-grandchildren.